          "id": "medmcqa-23a2836b-6cd0-41f7-ba28-586e6ad2315b",
          "text": "Due to an effective prevention program, the pre valence of an infectious disease in a community has been reduced by 90%. A physician continues to use the same diagnostic test for the disease that she has always used. How have the test’s characteristics changed?",
