          "text": "A 50-year-old obese man with hyperlipidemia, hypertension, and type 2 diabetes mellitus comes to the physician for a routine examination During the visit he asks, “What is my risk of having a heart attack?” \n\nWhile searching your information database, which of the following represents the best study design to address his question?",
