          "explanation": "Disadvantages of case control study Problems of bias relies on memory or past records Selection of an appropriate control group may be difficult Cannot measure incidence and can only estimate relative risk Do not distinguish between cause and associated factors Another major concern representatives of cases and control (refer pgno:74 park 23 rd edition)",
