          "explanation": "Overcrowding is the situation in which more people are living in a single dwelling thanthere is space for so that,the movemwnt is restricted,privacy secluded,hygiene impossible,rest and sleep difficult. The accepted stardards are -persons per room -floor space: according to floor space standard baby under 12 months is not counted and 1- 10 years is cointed as half a unit -sex sepaeration Parks textbook of preventive and social medicine.K Park. Edition 23.Pg no: 752",
